k Test (NBT) required for NWU admission in 2024?\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for NWU admission in 2024?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Table of Contents<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><a style=\"color: #008000;\" href=\"#_Toc80442613\">About the North West University (NWU) Online Application 2024<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><a style=\"color: #008000;\" href=\"#_Toc80442614\"><strong>How to Apply for NWU Application 2024<\/strong><\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><a style=\"color: #008000;\" href=\"#_Toc80442615\">Documents Required for NWU Online Application 2024<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><a style=\"color: #008000;\" href=\"#_Toc80442616\">NWU Application Fees 2024<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><a style=\"color: #008000;\" href=\"#_Toc80442617\">Application Deadline:<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><a style=\"color: #008000;\" href=\"#_Toc80442618\">Applying for Financial Assistance<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80442619\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for admission 2024?<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"about-the-north-west-university-nwu-online-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"About_the_North_West_University_NWU_Online_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80442613\"><\/a><span style=\"color: #008000;\">About the North West University (NWU) Online Application 2024<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This is to inform all and sundry that the management of the North-West University(NWU) is inviting applications from interested and suitably qualified students (Indigenes and International) for admission into undergraduate and postgraduate programmes for the 2024 academic year.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000;\">Before you apply, see the know the actual programs (Courses) available for the 2024 admission.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><a style=\"color: #008000;\" name=\"_Toc80442614\"><\/a><strong>How to Apply for NWU Application 2024<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Visit <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/vssweb.nwu.ac.za\/aaa-webclient\/UnsecuredLearnerEnquiriesWin.do#\/top\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\">here<\/span><\/span><\/a><\/strong><\/li>\n<li>select undergraduate\/postgraduate\/semester study abroad<\/li>\n<li>Create an Account with your valid email on the portal.<\/li>\n<li>Fill all necessary forms.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"documents-required-for-nwu-online-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Documents_Required_for_NWU_Online_Application_2024\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><a style=\"color: #008000;\" name=\"_Toc80442615\"><\/a>Documents Required for NWU Online Application 2024<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Valid Email<\/li>\n<li>South African Identity Number<\/li>\n<li>Passport Number (International Students)<\/li>\n<li><a href=\"http:\/\/studies.nwu.ac.za\/studies\/how-apply-online\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Click here to view all required documents<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"nwu-application-fees-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"NWU_Application_Fees_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80442616\"><\/a><span style=\"color: #008000;\">NWU Application Fees 2024<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Pay a Non-refundable application fee of R2 030 for South African citizens<\/li>\n<li>Pay a Non-refundable application fee for foreign citizens of R550<\/li>\n<li>Payments to be made before closing dates<\/li>\n<li>Ensure to use your Person Number or T Number as reference<\/li>\n<li><a href=\"http:\/\/services.nwu.ac.za\/student-accounts-and-bursaries\/payable-fees\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Click here to see all application fees guidelines<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-deadline\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_Deadline\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80442617\"><\/a><span style=\"color: #008000;\">Application Deadline:<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong><em>Take Note of These Dates<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Non-selection courses: \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 30 September 2024<\/li>\n<li>Music: \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 31 August 2024 &#8211; <strong>Also<\/strong> <a href=\"http:\/\/humanities.nwu.ac.za\/music\/applications\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">apply for an audition<\/a> before the closing date<\/li>\n<li>Graphic Design: \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 31 August 2024<\/li>\n<li>Engineering: \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u0